{"componentChunkName":"component---src-layouts-blog-post-layout-js","path":"/blog/how-to-share-a-shopify-unpublished-theme","result":{"pageContext":{"id":288,"date":"2021-01-04T05:28:30","date_gmt":"2021-01-04T05:28:30","guid":{"rendered":"https://www.ezfy.club/?p=288"},"modified":"2021-01-04T05:41:50","modified_gmt":"2021-01-04T05:41:50","slug":"how-to-share-a-shopify-unpublished-theme","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https://www.ezfy.club/how-to-share-a-shopify-unpublished-theme/","title":{"rendered":"How to share an unpublished Shopify theme&#8217;s preview"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Sometimes when you&#8217;re just testing things out or working on a particular thing in your theme you don&#8217;t want it visible to the public.<br><br>This is where &#8220;unpublished&#8221; or &#8220;offline&#8221; themes come in handy: they&#8217;re basically all the themes on your Shopify store that are not visible to the public.<br><br>However, what if you still want to share one of those unpublished themes with a friend, coworker or your developer? It&#8217;s possible and very easy to do.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Previewing the offline theme</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Firstly, from your Shopify admin, navigate to<strong> Online Store > Themes.</strong></li><li>Find the theme that you want to share and click on <strong>Actions > Preview.</strong><br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1915\" height=\"867\" class=\"wp-image-292\" style=\"width: 400px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/share-1.jpg\" alt=\"Instructions to how share an offline Shopify theme.\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/share-1.jpg 1915w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/share-1-600x272.jpg 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/share-1-1200x543.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/share-1-768x348.jpg 768w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/share-1-1536x695.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1915px) 100vw, 1915px\" /></li><li>On the new page that appeared, wait for a second and at the bottom of the screen you&#8217;ll see a bar pop up.</li><li>On this bar, click on the button <strong>Share Preview</strong> > <strong>Copy Link</strong>. <br><em>Note: Make sure you click on this button, do not share the URL on the top of your page because it won&#8217;t work.</em></li><li>Now just share the generated link with whoever you wish! <br></li></ol>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1200\" height=\"586\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/share-2-1200x586.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-294\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/share-2-1200x586.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/share-2-600x293.jpg 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/share-2-768x375.jpg 768w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/share-2-1536x750.jpg 1536w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/share-2.jpg 1919w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" /></figure>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Privately and quickly share unpublished Shopify themes&#8217; previews with your coworkers, developers or anyone else.</p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":299,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[9],"tags":[206,154],"image_alt":"","acf":[],"featured_image_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/how-share-600x271.jpg","featured_image_small_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/how-share-100x100.jpg","featured_image_large_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/how-share-1200x542.jpg","post_count":null,"categories_names":["Blog"],"tag_names":["all themes","Code Tutorial"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/288"}],"collection":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts"